QuestData.Title: Blue/Yellow Sprint 15 INTERNAL REPEATABLE
QuestData.Description: Ready for a tougher challenge? This one has an extra leg:$B$BRun through the arch...$BGet to the blue marker...$BGet to the green marker...$Bthen return here before the bell tolls 15 times.$B$BGood luck!
QuestData.LogDescription: Run through the arch, hit the blue marker, then the green marker, then return to the Ironelf games camp.
